{"tid":1541931,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［天理不容］St John救傷隊員竟以取笑盲眼義士為樂","createTime":"2019-09-04T16:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T10:37:56.000Z","uid":208984,"like":42,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"6cf5e6c98b4e339336592ff81346e2778afe9594","tid":1541931,"uid":208984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:52:34.000Z","msg":"話說剛剛小弟上緊連登個陣<br />\n發現到一個原本深藍但後來俾人屌得多變假黃既八婆<br />\n有興趣既可上去呢到睇<br />\n呢條女消費眼睛受傷女義士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536135\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536135</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n咁其實本來小弟都同事主都唔識既，只係見過一 兩次，但見既然都有勇者Po左，就一不做二不休啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eGcVRmL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeGcVRmL.jpg&h=3c068cd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大約6月頭既時間條八婆開左個咁既Po，屌尻班義士同護狗，咁我就唔清楚佢老豆老母有無做狗啦，一於有殺錯無放過。不過一岀po就俾各方既&rdquo;朋友&rdquo;屌，之後就一直都收左皮啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ekDmMVn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FekDmMVn.jpg&h=b3b261b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事後就有師兄/絲打開左上便個Post就話條八婆重要去抽人水，on9當有趣，一啲尊重都無，事後重要話係解釋嗰日個situation ，咁我唔理你因咩理由咁做，如果做完重要po story我就唔知你咩心態，完全無尊重過俾狗射爆眼個名好義士。<br />\n<br />\n話左部分惡行，最後就講小小條女既資料同J照啦<br />\n<br />\n全名:林殷彤<br />\n中學：荔景天主教中學<br />\n大學：東大幼教 已quit<br />\nFacebook：殷彤<br />\nInstagram：yannis0531<br />\nTG: @rexly<br />\n威水史：<br />\n參加saint john救傷隊 （九龍總區佐敦支隊 消費同為救傷既女義士<br />\n<br />\n尋晚發夢觀音菩薩俾既神秘號碼:<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">6494&nbsp;0363</span><br />\n絕對唔係電話號碼，千祈唔好半夜打去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UAnCkfK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUAnCkfK.jpg&h=6a4d40ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sji2wnq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSji2wnq.jpg&h=1f4b177b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ESEEyAM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FESEEyAM.jpg&h=5a166d9c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QF3YO86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQF3YO86.jpg&h=2b6cb30d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kwwrX2s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkwwrX2s.jpg&h=2f9b4112&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HqPtrVO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHqPtrVO.jpg&h=31f53e7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CBA4KHu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCBA4KHu.jpg&h=616243af&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ULz6VP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ULz6VP.jpg&h=9767178d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TnH3fPa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTnH3fPa.jpg&h=aa015fc7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wmRvFfQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwmRvFfQ.jpg&h=704537cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正所謂禍必及家人，上便個柒頭係佢條仔 重有個肥婆係佢老母。最後都係想講返句正經嘢先 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"cbffc032f9c987e2e172024be6a3d58aa0ca18b6","tid":1541931,"uid":208984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:56:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa82fa249d360d940a1a717a8e0b199f951ac5bd","tid":1541931,"uid":208984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:56:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b93d3b24f0d6f1c5bc10416edc506df30f48978a","tid":1541931,"uid":208984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:56:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5dbb862dd0247eef21405cd7faeb3fcffa659141","tid":1541931,"uid":208984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:57:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69d46d53ed24db7c7746c4b042bd74e99faf254e","tid":1541931,"uid":208984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:57:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd8085796932d0d6cd64341358b5d58ef0e0cce0","tid":1541931,"uid":208984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:57:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81c9bb2cd9e9f51a6e01a2571e2f7017528f06a3","tid":1541931,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:58:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"487a5250bb5b5b0949f6fc2fb1ae14e601335bd7","tid":1541931,"uid":315969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:00:21.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"fb019471e8f3ef8c88e0978ed9fed20ef8ea9d95","tid":1541931,"uid":139010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:00:23.000Z","msg":"Dllm 唉 食屎啦！ 懶撚得理佢！"},{"pid":"ff2e58038c428182d8f80047fa19ca2dfe598766","tid":1541931,"uid":203701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864f37d937e4e5137ac2c647842e88ff7601c709","tid":1541931,"uid":254461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:00:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a